These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, rugby, volleyball, snowboarding, sailing
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, bus, helicopter, subway, taxi
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, videographer, entrepreneur, accountant, police-officer
 1. the police-officer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the dressmaker is the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the accountant##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is between the chinese and the person driving the taxi##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Sport      | golf        | rugby | sailing     | volleyball   | snowboarding |
| Transport   | helicopter     | bus      | subway | taxi   | trike    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Job           | videographer | entrepreneur      | police-officer     | accountant   | dressmaker     |

