.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, rowing, weightlifting, basketball, soccer
5 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, frog, fish, hedgehog
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
House: ranch-style, victorian, futuristic, farmhouse, cottage
 1. the cottage house is in the middle##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the victorian house is between the chinese and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 6. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the indian is the owner of the fish##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the indian is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
12. the victorian house is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball | soccer    | rowing  | weightlifting    |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | mouse       | frog      | cat | fish        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| House     | futuristic    | victorian | cottage | farmhouse | ranch-style |

