.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, 7up, juice, sprite
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, rose, aconite, poppy
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, chef, architect, journalist
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the architect is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the paramedic##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the chef##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
10. the dancer is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the journalist##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
13. the journalist is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Beverage   | sprite  | almond-milk | water | juice | 7up        |
| Flower   | rose      | orchid      | aconite       | poppy       | tulip       |
| Job         | paramedic | journalist  | architect    | dancer    | chef        |

