.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
City: san-francisco, rome, prague, berlin, hamburg
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, apricot, lavender, blood-red, white
5 different games are played: chess, billiard, whist, monopoly, backgammon
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person playing monopoly and the person traveling to berlin##2
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the person who likes white is the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
10. the person playing monopoly is the british##1
11. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
12. the british is on the right of the person playing whist##1
13. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| City          | hamburg  | prague     | berlin   | rome     | san-francisco |
| Color         | white | aquamarine    | lavender  | blood-red | apricot   |
| Game   | billiard        | chess    | backgammon     | whist     | monopoly    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

