The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat, frog, turtle, ferret
 1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person driving the car is between the owner of the goat and the person who growspoppy##2
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growslily##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person who growslily is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Transport   | trike       | train       | bike   | car      | motorbike    |
