5 different games are played: poker, whist, backgammon, chess, scrabble
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing, skiing, volleyball
 1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person who likes pink is between the fan of trance and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the fan of electronic is between the fan of trance and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person playing chess##1
13. the fan of trance is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Color      | apricot  | pink      | purple   | lavender   | emerald   |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | electronic   | blues   | techno | rock     |
