The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, folk, techno, salsa, d&b
There 5 different types of food: corn, orange, peach, zucchini, cucumber
 1. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of d&b is the person eating orange##1
 4. the fan of techno is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person traveling to miami##2
 5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
 9. the fan of salsa is the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the fan of techno is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | fishing   | photography | skydiving  | collecting | magic-tricks |
| City   | boston | berlin     | miami   | new-york     | marseilles      |
