 5. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the security-guard##1
 7. the nurse is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
11. the photographer is between the townhouse house and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Food    | pineapple       | papaya    | apricot | cucumber  | grapefruit        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| House       | townhouse        | ranch-style   | palace  | gothic-revival   | cottage |
| Job   | coach       | photographer      | dressmaker      | nurse | security-guard  |

