.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
5 different games are played: bridge, go, mah-jongg, scrabble, billiard
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, board-games, hiking, baking, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, may, october, november, april
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person playing billiard and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Game           | go | mah-jongg | scrabble | billiard    | bridge  |
| Hobby   | baking  | board-games    | dancing | hiking    | woodworking |
| Birthday   | october  | may        | january   | november    | april     |

