 3. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person drinking mirinda and the havana-smoker##2
 8. the game-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
