.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, light-blue, fuchsia, green, pink
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, september, june, july, october
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, ice-hockey, badminton, climbing
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who likes green is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Color         | fuchsia    | pink  | light-blue  | yellow      | green |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Birthday   | june | january    | october    | july       | september         |
| Sport   | badminton  | snowboarding | climbing    | ice-hockey     | cricket      |

 